Class CONSTANT_Utf8_info

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.coffi.cp_info
      • soot.coffi.CONSTANT_Utf8_info

  • public class CONSTANT_Utf8_info
extends cp_info
    A constant pool entry of type CONSTANT_Utf8; note this is not multithread safe. It is, however, immutable.
